# ====================================================================
# KiCad 9 Recommended Gitignore
# ====================================================================

# --- Temporary & Backup Files ---
*.000
*.bak
*.bck
*.kicad_pcb-bak
*.kicad_sch-bak
*.sch-bak
*~
~*.lck
_autosave-*
\#*#
*.tmp

# --- KiCad 9 Project Backups Directory ---
# KiCad 9 creates a local directory to auto-save zip backups of your work
*-backups/

# --- Local User Preferences & Caches ---
# Contains your personal workspace settings, window positions, etc.
# Highly recommended to ignore so it doesn't cause constant Git conflicts.
*.kicad_prl
fp-info-cache

# --- Netlist & Autorouter Files (Rarely needed in version control) ---
*.net
*.dsn
*.ses

# --- Design Rule Check (DRC) Reports ---
*.rpt

# --- Manufacturing & Output Directories (Optional but Recommended) ---
# If you prefer to save your Gerbers and BOMs in specific folders, 
# uncomment these lines to keep your repository clean.
# Gerber/
# GBR/
# Output/
# _saved_boms/